overview: Our Professional Massage Therapy video class, taught by an instructor with over 20 years of teaching experience, will prepare massage students to take state certification tests. While each state has different certification or registration procedures for therapists, the principles and knowledge are the same. Instead of enrolling in a professional massage therapy school taking many months and hundreds of dollars in fees you'll learn the techniques of massage therapy in the comfort of your home, saving you both time and money!
title: Massage Therapy for Professionals
